text: Milan Dimun (born 19 September 1996) is a Slovak footballer who currently plays for Ekstraklasa club Cracovia as a midfielder. ==Club career== ===MFK Košice=== Dimun made his professional Fortuna Liga's debut for MFK Košice on 18 October 2014 against FC ViOn Zlaté Moravce.ZLATÉ MORAVCE VS. KOŠICE 3 - 0 18.10.2014, soccerway.com === Cracovia === On 10 June 2016 he signed a four- year deal with Cracovia. ==References== ==External links== * MFK Košice profile * * Futbalnet profile * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FC VSS Košice players Category:KS Cracovia players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:Ekstraklasa players Category:Expatriate footballers in Poland Category:Slovak expatriate sportspeople in Poland Category:Sportspeople from Košice
